      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "We should frame this as a \"data exposure incident\" rather than a \"breach,\" as that term implies unauthorized access by malicious actors, which isn't the case here. The internal error was a simple, temporary configuration oversight that we corrected immediately, demonstrating our robust internal controls. We will emphasize the swift remediation and the minimal scope, assuring the public that the data was never compromised by external threats.",
